headline: Franklin Templeton Canada Announces Final December ETF Cash Distributions and Annual Reinvested Distributions
summary: Franklin Templeton Canada today announced the final December 2024 cash distributions and the annual reinvested distributions for its ETFs and ETF series of mutual funds available to Canadian investors. This is an update to the estimated December 2024 cash distributions and annual reinvested distributions previously announced on December 20, 2024.

headline: My Best Dividend Aristocrats For January 2025
summary: The ProShares S&P 500 Dividend Aristocrat ETF rocked a cool 4.85% gain in November, but it's giving up nearly half of its return this year in December. Read more here.
